#: ../../../reference/module_structure.rst:7
msgid ""
"NumPy has a large number of submodules. Most regular usage of NumPy requires "
"only the main namespace and a smaller set of submodules. The rest either "
"have special-purpose or niche namespaces."
msgstr ""

